data.description: The home you've been waiting for at a price you can afford. 3 teen-sized bedrooms plus a secluded primary bedroom on the main level. Features new luxury vinyl plank flooring, all new kitchen with new appliances, new paint, carpet, some new fixtures, new bathroom upstairs, you will love the extra space of the front porch! Huge backyard with an additional garage and space to build more, everything within walking distance, lots of closet space, see it today!
